rdf:Description.dc:title: vid119_0601c-- Point coverage of sediment types from video collected from the Delta submersible vehicle.
rdf:Description.dc:description: The Delta submersible vehicle, outfitted with video equipment (and other devices), was deployed from the R/V Auriga during September 2001 to monitor seafloor disturbance and benthic recovery after installation of the PC1 fiber optic cables.
